body:
### Hatsize

## WordPress: Easy PDF Embed
This WordPress plugin allows you to easily embed a PDF, relying on [PDF.js](http://mozilla.github.io/pdf.js/) for HTML5 capable browsers with a Java Applet fallback.

## Support or Contact
Please submit all issues to the appropriate GitHub repo [issue tracker](https://guides.github.com/features/issues/).
